Doc: The specification of, for American-style digitals, whether the trigger level must be touched or not touched.

Source.Contents:
/#
 The specification of, for American-style digitals, whether the trigger level must be touched or not touched.
 #/
enum FpML5.pretrade.TouchConditionEnum {
    # The spot rate must have touched the predetermined trigger rate at any time over the life of the option for the payout to occur.
    Touch 
    # The spot rate has not touched the predetermined trigger rate at any time over the life of the option for the payout to occur.
    Notouch 

}

Touch.Doc: The spot rate must have touched the predetermined trigger rate at any time over the life of the option for the payout to occur.
Touch.Name: Touch

Notouch.Doc: The spot rate has not touched the predetermined trigger rate at any time over the life of the option for the payout to occur.
Notouch.Name: Notouch
